name: Get out of my field!
description:
Take your tanks out, someone is fighting for your field and this is a small world!

Get out of my field! is an arcade action game made for the ludum dare 38 by a team of 3 developers, where 2 players have to fight for the field with tanks until the other one falls out.

So take the controller and kick the intruder out of your f***ing field!
